balidaan ( english : sacrifice ) is a 1985 bollywood , action film produced by salim on aftab pictures pvt ltd banner , directed by s.a.chandra shekaran . starring jeetendra , sridevi in the lead roles and music composed by bappi lahari . the film is remake of telugu movie balidanam ( 1982 ) , starring sobhan babu , madhavi in pivotal roles .